(2958, 2, '2013-08-27 17:18:37', '2013-08-27 17:18:37', 'This summer I went to Indonesia once again. I went back because of all those perfect surfspots. Due to pretty much no swell during the two weeks I was there, I had lots of time to point my camera at everything else I like about this country.\n\n<a href="http://vimeo.com/72911992">http://vimeo.com/72911992</a>\n\nNext to all the picture perfect moments we tourists experience in this country, there are the local people who make all this happen for us. I started to stroll through cities and tried to capture the daily grind of the locals.\nI appreciate that the local people showed me their world and let me experience Indonesia in a new way.\n\nTERIMA KASIH!', 'INDOVISTA - one trip. two perspectives.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hello-world-2', '', '', '2013-08-27 17:18:37', '2013-08-27 17:18:37', '', 0, 'http://codehaiku.co/?p=1', 0, 'post', '', 1),
